      "date": "2013-06-06 20:41:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: (1 inline comment)\n\nJinshan, could you please also remind me what are the latest rules on when the layout is packed in the completion AST? Is it only when the layout is released?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "818296af5db61695f139e9a7194f692aef73d0c5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 4,
        "name": "Jinshan Xiong",
        "email": "jinshan.xiong@intel.com",
        "username": "Jay",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-06-06 22:08:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: (1 inline comment)\n\n\"Jinshan, could you please also remind me what are the latest rules on when the layout is packed in the completion AST? Is it only when the layout is released?\"\n\nRight now, when a layout lock is enqueued, layout can be returned in 2 ways:\n1. if the MDT can grant the layout immediately, layout will be packed in DLM_LVB of lock reply RPC;\n2. Otherwise, client has to fetch layout in ll_layout_fetch()",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
